  PROC_ERROR_FUNCTIONS_015:
    error_code: 1064
    category: PROCEDURE
    applies_to: [PROCEDURE, FUNCTION]
    regex: "ERROR_(MESSAGE|SEVERITY|STATE|NUMBER|LINE)\\("
    cause: "MSSQL ERROR_*() 함수 — MySQL 미지원"
    fix_type: prompt_injection
    fix_prompt: |
      [PROCEDURE 전용] MSSQL 시스템 함수 → MySQL DIAGNOSTICS.

